         1. Header: System overview based on Section 1.
         2. Topology Visualizer (Canvas): Interactive node map representing the concepts in Section 1 and 2. Users select nodes to view PeerState.
         3. Scoring Algorithm Lab: Interactive sliders implementing the formula in Section 3.1. Visualized with Chart.js.
         4. Logic & Data Reference: Cards explaining HandleAdvertise and HealthCheck (Section 3.2, 3.3) and Data Structures (Section 4).
         This structure moves from the high-level network view down to the specific algorithmic logic, facilitating understanding of the system's "Brain".
    -->

